WEBVTT

00:01.697 --> 00:03.307
PREVIOUSLY
ON "THE MENTALIST"...

00:03.351 --> 00:04.700
YEAH, LENA'S
ON A SHORT LIST

00:04.743 --> 00:05.875
FOR A POSITION IN
THE COMMERCE DEPARTMENT IN D.C.,

00:05.918 --> 00:06.919
SO WE'RE CELEBRATING.

00:06.963 --> 00:08.486
IT'S NOT A DONE DEAL YET.

00:08.530 --> 00:10.488
I HAVE TO BE CONFIRMED,
AND THAT COULD TAKE MONTHS.

00:10.532 --> 00:13.013
WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME
ABOUT RIO BRAVO STATION?

00:13.056 --> 00:15.711
I DON'T THINK I WANT
TO GO TO D.C.
WHY?

00:15.754 --> 00:17.626
BECAUSE YOU'RE GOING TO BE
ASKED QUESTIONS,

00:17.669 --> 00:20.020
AND IF ANY OF THOSE QUESTIONS
INVOLVE RIO BRAVO,

00:20.063 --> 00:21.673
THEN YOU NEED
TO BE ABLE TO SAY

00:21.717 --> 00:23.806
THAT YOU DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

00:25.547 --> 00:27.940
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

00:27.984 --> 00:30.160
Man: HI, FOLKS.
WELCOME TO ALAMO BREWHOUSE.

00:30.204 --> 00:32.206
CHRISTINE WILL SHOW YOU
TO YOUR TABLE.

00:32.249 --> 00:33.816
HEY, GUYS.
COME ON AND JOIN US.

00:33.859 --> 00:36.601
WE HAVE A GREAT CHILEAN SEA BASS
TODAY FOR YOU GUYS.

00:36.645 --> 00:38.821
SIT YOU RIGHT OVER HERE.

00:41.171 --> 00:44.740
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

00:51.268 --> 00:53.140
D.E.A.! SEARCH WARRANT!

00:53.183 --> 00:54.358
COME ON, LET ME SEE SOME HANDS!

00:54.402 --> 00:56.317
PUT YOUR HANDS
ON THE TABLE!

00:56.360 --> 00:57.840
D.E.A.! POLICíA! POLICíA!

00:57.883 --> 00:59.755
DOWN ON THE GROUND NOW!

00:59.798 --> 01:01.322
HEAD DOWN ON THE GROUND NOW!

01:01.365 --> 01:02.932
HANDS BEHIND YOUR HEAD!

01:02.975 --> 01:05.152
SIT!WHAT'S GOING ON?

01:05.195 --> 01:07.154
WE HAVE A WARRANT TO
SEARCH THESE PREMISES
FOR ILLEGAL NARCOTICS.

01:07.197 --> 01:08.938
NARCOT--
THIS IS A RESTAURANT.

01:08.981 --> 01:11.158
SIR, READ THE WARRANT.
LET ME DO MY JOB, OKAY?

01:11.201 --> 01:12.811
LET'S GO TALK IN MY OFFICE.

01:12.855 --> 01:14.161
OH, YOU WANT TO GO
TO YOUR OFFICE?
LET'S TALK.

01:14.204 --> 01:15.379
YEAH, LET'S DO THAT.
LET'S START THERE.

01:15.423 --> 01:19.688
[ DOG SNIFFING,
GROWLING SOFTLY ]

01:21.690 --> 01:23.561
WHAT DO YOU GOT,
OROSCO?

01:23.605 --> 01:25.955
YEAH, WE SEARCHED THE OFFICE,
DINING ROOM, FREEZER.

01:25.998 --> 01:27.783
K9 WENT THROUGH EVERYTHING.
WE GOT NOTHING.

01:27.826 --> 01:30.133
OKAY, SEARCH AGAIN.
OKAY.

01:30.177 --> 01:32.614
Korbell: DON'T WALK AWAY.
I'M TALKING TO YOU.

01:32.657 --> 01:34.790
MR. KORBELL, WE ARE GOING
TO FINISH OUR SEARCH.THIS IS HARASSMENT!

01:34.833 --> 01:36.618
THE MORE YOU INTERFERE,
THE LONGER IT'S GONNA TAKE.

01:36.661 --> 01:39.099
WHO'S GOING TO CLEAN
THIS PLACE UP? HUH?

01:39.142 --> 01:40.883
I'M TALKING TO YOU, BITCH!HEY!

01:40.926 --> 01:42.493
[ BOTH PANTING ]

01:42.537 --> 01:44.843
OKAY.

01:44.887 --> 01:47.237
DON'T TALK TO MY AGENT
THAT WAY. HMM?

01:47.281 --> 01:49.674
OKAY, EASY.

01:49.718 --> 01:51.720
Peterson: GONZALEZ.

01:58.640 --> 02:01.121
PACK UP
AND GET OUT OF HERE.

02:01.164 --> 02:03.340
I'M WATCHING YOU, PAL.

02:03.384 --> 02:05.168
LITTLE DOG,
PUT YOUR HANDS ON ME?

02:11.957 --> 02:13.829
[ METAL DETECTOR BEEPS ]

02:18.486 --> 02:21.706
EXCUSE ME.
I'M LOOKING FOR BILL PETERSON.

02:21.750 --> 02:23.621
THERE HE IS RIGHT THERE.

02:23.665 --> 02:25.710
Peterson: [ Chuckling ] HEY!HEY.

02:25.754 --> 02:27.364
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

02:27.408 --> 02:29.410
DENNIS.
YOU LOOK GOOD.

02:29.453 --> 02:30.976
AH.
YOU LOST WEIGHT.

02:31.020 --> 02:33.283
OH, YEAH,
A LITTLE BIT. THANKS.

02:33.327 --> 02:35.459
HOW'S LENA?
OH. SHE'S IN D.C.

02:35.503 --> 02:36.765
BIG THINGS DOING.

02:36.808 --> 02:38.027
REALLY?
OH, YEAH.

02:38.070 --> 02:40.551
OH, GOOD FOR HER.

02:40.595 --> 02:45.077
SO, DENNIS ABBOTT IS HANDLING
THE AFTER ACTION REPORT

02:45.121 --> 02:48.907
ON MY TEAM'S FAILED RAID
ON ALAMO BREWHOUSE.

02:48.951 --> 02:50.431
YEAH, WELL, D.C. ASKED.

02:50.474 --> 02:53.216
YOU KNOW, THEY WANT SOMEONE
OUTSIDE OF D.E.A.

02:53.260 --> 02:56.045
LOOK, I DON'T WANT THIS
TO BE AWKWARD.
WHY?

02:56.088 --> 02:59.701
BECAUSE WHEN YOU WORKED FOR ME,
YOU WERE BARELY SHAVING?

02:59.744 --> 03:02.225
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

03:02.269 --> 03:05.446
[ CHUCKLES ] IT'S BEEN A LONG
TIME SINCE RIO BRAVO STATION.

03:05.489 --> 03:07.535
YOU'VE COME UP
IN THE WORLD.

03:07.578 --> 03:10.102
STILL,
WE DID SOME GOOD WORK.

03:10.146 --> 03:12.496
YES, WE DID.

03:12.540 --> 03:15.412
SO, LOOK, I AM GOING TO NEED
TO TALK TO YOUR PEOPLE

03:15.456 --> 03:16.761
AND TAKE A LOOK
AT THE FILES.

03:16.805 --> 03:18.067
HAVE AT IT.

03:18.110 --> 03:20.200
ALAMO BREWHOUSE
WAS JUST BAD LUCK.

03:20.243 --> 03:23.115
AND YOU DIDN'T FIND
ANY DRUGS?

03:23.159 --> 03:25.727
DIFFERENT DAY,
WE WOULD HAVE.

03:25.770 --> 03:28.904
I WANT TO START WITH THE AGENT
WHO LED THE RAID, GONZALEZ.

03:28.947 --> 03:31.428
I UNDERSTAND
THAT THE RESTAURANT OWNER

03:31.472 --> 03:33.169
FILED A COMPLAINT
AGAINST HIM.

03:33.213 --> 03:36.738
[ SIGHS ] GONZO GOT A LITTLE
OVERHEATED, YOU KNOW.

03:36.781 --> 03:38.609
HE'S ON
ADMINISTRATIVE LEAVE.

03:38.653 --> 03:42.004
I'LL, UH, I'LL GET YOU
HIS HOME ADDRESS.

03:42.047 --> 03:44.441
UM, DENNIS,
I'M GONNA WANT TO TAKE A LOOK

03:44.485 --> 03:47.227
AT THAT REPORT
OF YOURS BEFORE IT GOES IN.

03:50.055 --> 03:53.450
WELL, YOU KNOW, THAT'S NOT
HOW WE DO THINGS, BILL.

03:53.494 --> 03:56.018
A LOT OF PEOPLE
IN THIS AGENCY

03:56.061 --> 03:59.151
GOT THEIR GUNSIGHTS SET
FOR OL' BILL PETERSON.

03:59.195 --> 04:02.459
I NEED TO KNOW IF YOU'RE HANDING
'EM ANY BULLETS.

04:02.503 --> 04:05.810
WELL, I'M SORRY.
MY HANDS ARE TIED.

04:05.854 --> 04:09.292
WHEN I WAS YOUR BOSS AT
RIO BRAVO, I HAD YOUR BACK.

04:09.336 --> 04:12.295
YOU'RE TELLING ME
YOU DON'T HAVE MINE NOW?

04:12.339 --> 04:14.776
IS THAT HOW YOU WANT
TO PLAY THIS?

04:14.819 --> 04:17.692
COME ON.

04:17.735 --> 04:20.521
I'M JUST LOOKING FOR A LITTLE
PROFESSIONAL COURTESY.

04:23.785 --> 04:26.309
I'LL SEE WHAT I CAN DO,
BILL.

04:26.353 --> 04:29.356
ALL RIGHT. [ LAUGHS ]

04:29.399 --> 04:30.574
THANKS.

04:38.756 --> 04:40.018
LENA:
I don't understand

04:40.062 --> 04:41.846
why you have to write
the damn report.

04:41.890 --> 04:43.065
OH, IT'S NOTHING.

04:43.108 --> 04:44.545
I'LL WRITE IT,
D.C. WILL IGNORE IT,

04:44.588 --> 04:46.286
AND WE'LL GET ON
WITH OUR LIVES.

04:46.329 --> 04:48.462
How are you, baby?
GOOD.

04:48.505 --> 04:49.767
I JUST HAD LUNCH
WITH A SENATOR.

04:49.811 --> 04:51.203
I'M MEETING WITH THE CHAIR

04:51.247 --> 04:52.248
OF THE ENERGY AND COMMERCE
COMMITTEE IN AN HOUR.

04:52.292 --> 04:53.380
It's exciting.

04:53.423 --> 04:55.382
OH.
I WISH I WERE THERE.

04:55.425 --> 04:56.687
I'll call you tonight,
okay?

04:56.731 --> 04:57.514
I LOVE YOU.

04:57.558 --> 04:59.429
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

04:59.473 --> 05:02.302
[ Click ]

05:33.855 --> 05:36.161
[ SPANISH TV CHATTER ]

05:39.948 --> 05:41.166
FBI!

05:41.210 --> 05:43.952
AGENT GONZALEZ,
ARE YOU IN HERE?

05:47.172 --> 05:50.045
[ TV CHATTER CONTINUES ]

06:15.592 --> 06:18.595
ABBOTT SAID IT WAS THE DEATH
OF A D.E.A. AGENT.

06:18.639 --> 06:21.119
BY THE WAY,
KEEP TOMORROW NIGHT OPEN.

06:21.163 --> 06:22.643
WHY WOULD IT BE CLOSED?

06:22.686 --> 06:24.384
YOUR BIRTHDAY.

06:24.427 --> 06:25.950
OH, THAT.YES.

06:25.994 --> 06:27.822
I ALREADY TOLD EVERYBODY
AT WORK --

06:27.865 --> 06:29.432
NO SONGS,
NO CAKE, NO GIFTS.

06:29.476 --> 06:30.955
GOOD. THANK YOU.
EXCEPT ME.

06:30.999 --> 06:32.479
OH, YOU HAVE
A GIFT FOR ME?

06:32.522 --> 06:33.915
IT'S A SURPRISE.

06:33.958 --> 06:36.439
A SURPRISE?
THAT'S RIGHT.

06:36.483 --> 06:39.442
YOU THINK YOU CAN KEEP A SECRET
FROM ME FOR THAT LONG?

06:39.486 --> 06:42.706
I DON'T THINKI CAN.
I KNOWI CAN.

06:42.750 --> 06:45.317
I ADMIRE YOUR CONFIDENCE.

06:45.361 --> 06:48.320
♪♪♪

06:48.364 --> 06:51.367
--Captions by VITAC--
www.vitac.com

06:55.545 --> 06:58.548
SO, VEGA, I'VE GOT TICKETS
TO THAT BLUES FESTIVAL,

06:58.592 --> 07:01.072
AND I WAS WONDERING...

07:01.116 --> 07:03.335
NOT "VEGA." MICHELLE.

07:03.379 --> 07:07.688
MICHELLE, I'VE GOT TICKETS,
AND I WAS --

07:07.731 --> 07:09.646
HEY.

07:09.690 --> 07:11.213
HI.

07:11.256 --> 07:12.736
YOU OKAY?

07:12.780 --> 07:14.346
YEAH.

07:14.390 --> 07:15.870
SO, UM, MICHELLE --

07:15.913 --> 07:17.480
ABBOTT WANTS US.
CAUGHT A CASE.

07:17.524 --> 07:20.048
O-OKAY. GREAT.
YEAH, I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

07:20.091 --> 07:21.528
OKAY.

07:24.705 --> 07:26.881
GOOD MORNING, EVERYONE.

07:26.924 --> 07:30.014
THIS IS BILL PETERSON,
SAN ANTONIO D.E.A.

07:30.058 --> 07:32.887
OUR VICTIM'S NAME
IS DARRELL GONZALEZ.

07:32.930 --> 07:35.193
HE'S BEEN WITH THE D.E.A.
FOR SEVEN YEARS.

07:35.237 --> 07:37.108
SERVED IN AFGHANISTAN
BEFORE THAT.

07:37.152 --> 07:40.808
I WANT YOU ALL TO KNOW HOW MUCH
I APPRECIATE YOUR HELP.

07:43.027 --> 07:46.466
WE'RE GONNA GET THE PIGS
WHO DID THIS.

07:46.509 --> 07:51.296
WE UNDERSTAND HOW HARD IT IS
TO LOSE SOMEBODY.

07:51.340 --> 07:54.430
WE WILL EXTEND EVERY COURTESY
TO YOU.

07:54.474 --> 07:55.910
EVERY COURTESY?

07:55.953 --> 07:57.868
THAT'S THE SOSA CARTEL TAG.

07:57.912 --> 08:00.828
LOOKS LIKE THEY'RE TRYING
TO SEND A MESSAGE.

08:00.871 --> 08:03.352
GONZO HAD JUST LED A RAID
ON A RESTAURANT

08:03.395 --> 08:05.615
THAT WAS DISTRIBUTING
SOSA NARCOTICS.

08:05.659 --> 08:07.530
AND IT WAS OWNED
BY THISMAN.

08:07.574 --> 08:10.315
STEVEN KORBELL.

08:10.359 --> 08:12.404
HOW DOES A RESTAURANT OWNER
BECOME A DRUG DEALER?

08:12.448 --> 08:14.537
HE USED TO MANAGE A HOTEL
IN MEXICO CITY

08:14.581 --> 08:16.147
THAT WAS OWNED
BY THE SOSAS.

08:16.191 --> 08:18.236
THAT'S WHEN HE BEGAN WORKING
WITH THEM.

08:18.280 --> 08:21.196
IN THE RAID THAT GONZALEZ LED,
THEY DIDN'T FIND ANYTHING.

08:21.239 --> 08:24.504
WHY WOULD KORBELL ORDER A HIT
AFTER AN UNSUCCESSFUL RAID?

08:24.547 --> 08:26.506
I MEAN, IT JUST CALLS
MORE ATTENTION TO HIM.

08:26.549 --> 08:27.898
EXACTLY.

08:27.942 --> 08:29.596
THE ANIMAL
THAT ESCAPES A SNARE

08:29.639 --> 08:31.728
DOESN'T NECESSARILY
GO AFTER THE POACHER.

08:31.772 --> 08:34.731
OKAY, EVERYONE, WE CAN ASK
THESE QUESTIONS IN SAN ANTONIO.

08:34.775 --> 08:37.038
SO, SADDLE UP.

08:46.874 --> 08:49.137
WHAT DOES THIS GUY PETERSON
HAVE ON YOU?

08:49.180 --> 08:50.747
WHY DO YOU ASK?

08:50.791 --> 08:53.358
BECAUSE YOU'RE ACTING LIKE
HE HAS SOMETHING ON YOU.

08:53.402 --> 08:55.883
HE DOESN'T.

08:55.926 --> 08:58.842
OKAY.

09:08.722 --> 09:10.724
Patrick:
GONZALEZ'S DESK?

09:10.767 --> 09:12.203
YEAH, WE WERE NEIGHBORS.

09:12.247 --> 09:14.858
MAN, HE USED TO LISTEN
TO THE WORST MUSIC.

09:14.902 --> 09:16.294
SMOOTH JAZZ.

09:16.338 --> 09:17.818
LET'S SEE.

09:17.861 --> 09:19.994
ALAMO BREWHOUSE FILE.

09:20.037 --> 09:21.778
YEAH.
THAT'S THOROUGH.

09:21.822 --> 09:23.432
YEAH,
HE DIDN'T TALK COMPUTERS.

09:23.475 --> 09:25.129
HE KEPT A HARD COPY
ON EVERYTHING --

09:25.173 --> 09:26.609
FINANCIAL RECORDS,

09:26.653 --> 09:28.742
WITNESS INTERVIEWS,
SURVEILLANCE PHOTOS.

09:28.785 --> 09:31.222
MM. MY KIND OF PEOPLE.
YOU MIND IF I TAKE A LOOK?

09:31.266 --> 09:33.311
DIG IN.
THANK YOU.

09:38.926 --> 09:40.318
HOW LONG
HAD AGENT GONZALEZ

09:40.362 --> 09:42.407
BEEN INVESTIGATING
THE ALAMO BREWHOUSE?

09:42.451 --> 09:43.887
MONTHS.

09:43.931 --> 09:45.367
GONZO
WAS RELENTLESS.

09:45.410 --> 09:47.630
HE SLEPT HERE ON THE COUCH
HALF THE WEEK.

09:47.674 --> 09:50.851
AGENT BORDICK, YOU WERE
THE ANALYST WORKING WITH HIM?

09:50.894 --> 09:52.243
WHAT ARE YOU IMPLYING?

09:52.287 --> 09:53.897
I'M IMPLYING YOU WERE

09:53.941 --> 09:55.159
THE ANALYST
WORKING WITH HIM.

09:55.203 --> 09:56.944
WE HAD THIS ONE RIGHT.

09:56.987 --> 09:59.120
THAT RESTAURANT WAS A FRONT,

09:59.163 --> 10:01.470
AND WE MUST'VE JUST MISSED
THE SUPPLY RE-UP.

10:01.513 --> 10:03.690
Vega: THIS WASN'T YOUR
FIRST TIME COMING UP EMPTY.

10:03.733 --> 10:05.256
YOUR TEAM'S HAD OTHER MISSES.

10:05.300 --> 10:08.303
HOW LONG HAVE THE TWO OF YOU
BEEN OUT OF THE ACADEMY?

10:08.346 --> 10:10.000
AN HOUR?
WHOA.

10:10.044 --> 10:12.307
EASY, JEFF.Vega: IT'S OKAY, AGENT OROSCO.

10:12.350 --> 10:15.919
WE'D BE HAPPY TO SEND YOU
OUR CVs IF YOU LIKE.

10:19.227 --> 10:21.925
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

10:26.451 --> 10:28.584
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

10:30.847 --> 10:33.328
DID YOU HAVE ANY CONTACT
WITH GONZALEZ

10:33.371 --> 10:36.810
IN THE DAYS FOLLOWING THE RAID,
A-AFTER HE WAS ON LEAVE?

10:36.853 --> 10:38.899
NO. NO,
BUT THAT WASN'T UNUSUAL.

10:38.942 --> 10:40.552
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT HE WAS DOING?

10:40.596 --> 10:41.989
KNOWING GONZO,
HE WAS PROBABLY OBSESSING

10:42.032 --> 10:43.773
OVER WHY THAT RAID
WENT SOUTH.

10:43.817 --> 10:46.036
EXCUSE ME. THAT'S THE FRONT
OF THE RESTAURANT, RIGHT?

10:46.080 --> 10:48.212
YEAH. THOSE ARE
THE SURVEILLANCE PHOTOS.

10:48.256 --> 10:49.736
TAKEN OVER A FEW DAYS?

10:49.779 --> 10:51.085
NO, WE STAKED IT OUT
FOR A FEW WEEKS.

10:51.128 --> 10:52.826
EXCELLENT.

10:52.869 --> 10:54.828
YOU KNOW WHERE THE OWNER
OF THE RESTAURANT IS?HE'S HERE.

10:54.871 --> 10:57.831
HE'S TALKING TO CHO
AND ONE OF THE D.E.A. AGENTS.

10:59.441 --> 11:01.443
WHAT'S HE DOING?

11:01.486 --> 11:03.663
MR. KORBELL
IS A COMMUNITY PILLAR.

11:03.706 --> 11:06.317
HE SPONSORS CHILI COOK-OFFS
AND YOUTH BASEBALL TEAMS.

11:06.361 --> 11:08.015
HE'S NOT A KILLER.

11:08.058 --> 11:10.104
HE'S GOT A HELL OF A P.R.
DEPARTMENT, I'LL GIVE HIM THAT.

11:10.147 --> 11:12.628
WHERE WERE YOU YESTERDAY
FROM 8:00 A.M. TO 3:00 P.M.?

11:12.672 --> 11:16.153
IN DALLAS.
I HAD BUSINESS.

11:16.197 --> 11:18.068
PRODUCE EVIDENCE OF A CRIME,
GENTLEMEN.

11:18.112 --> 11:20.418
SO FAR YOU'VE DONE A BANG-UP JOB
OF THE OPPOSITE.

11:20.462 --> 11:23.639
HI. PATRICK JANE. FBI.

11:23.683 --> 11:24.640
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

11:24.684 --> 11:25.728
HEY, CHO.

11:25.772 --> 11:27.077
HI, JANE.

11:27.121 --> 11:28.644
KORBELL?YEAH.

11:28.688 --> 11:29.950
VERY IMPORTANT QUESTION.

11:29.993 --> 11:31.952
WHAT TIME DOES
YOUR RESTAURANT OPEN?

11:34.694 --> 11:36.173
NOON.

11:36.217 --> 11:38.915
SO YOU'LL BE OPENING
IN A LITTLE UNDER AN HOUR.

11:38.959 --> 11:40.525
IF I'M NOT WASTING
MY TIME HERE, YEAH.

11:40.569 --> 11:42.484
UH, THESE TWO
ARE FREE TO GO.

11:42.527 --> 11:44.007
HEY!HAVE A LOVELY AFTERNOON.

11:44.051 --> 11:45.487
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

11:45.530 --> 11:47.315
YOU CAN'T DO THIS, MAN.

11:47.358 --> 11:48.969
YES, HE CAN.
YOU CAN GO.

12:00.328 --> 12:01.764
HEY.

12:01.808 --> 12:04.158
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS,
MAN?

12:04.201 --> 12:05.812
EASY, TIGER.

12:05.855 --> 12:07.248
FBI IS SENDING A TEAM IN

12:07.291 --> 12:08.858
TO RAID THAT RESTAURANT
THIS AFTERNOON.

12:08.902 --> 12:10.860
IF WE FIND DRUGS, WE WANT TO
MAKE SURE KORBELL'S THERE.

12:10.904 --> 12:12.819
WHY DIDN'T ANYBODY TELL US?

12:12.862 --> 12:14.951
WHAT DID I JUST DO?

12:21.262 --> 12:23.090
HEY.

12:23.133 --> 12:26.354
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA BELIEVE
WHAT THIS GUY JUST TOLD ME.

12:54.948 --> 12:58.081
CARE TO TELL ME
WHY WE'RE HERE?

12:58.125 --> 12:59.300
OF COURSE.

12:59.343 --> 13:00.823
IN THREE MINUTES.

13:00.867 --> 13:02.912
HOW DO YOU KNOW PETERSON?

13:02.956 --> 13:04.479
I WORKED FOR HIM.

13:04.522 --> 13:05.959
A LONG TIME AGO.

13:06.002 --> 13:08.657
YOU MUST'VE BEEN
VERYGREEN.

13:08.700 --> 13:10.441
OH, YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

13:10.485 --> 13:12.182
AGENT PETERSON.

13:13.749 --> 13:14.837
WERE YOUR EARS BURNING?

13:14.881 --> 13:18.014
DENNIS. WHAT'S UP?

13:18.058 --> 13:20.190
YOU'RE RAIDING
ALAMO BREWHOUSE?

13:20.234 --> 13:22.279
NO.THIS ONE HERE

13:22.323 --> 13:24.978
TOLD MY PEOPLE YOU'RE SENDING IN
A STRIKE TEAM.

13:25.021 --> 13:26.936
I DID. SORRY.

13:26.980 --> 13:29.025
THAT WAS A LIE.
WHAT?

13:29.069 --> 13:31.506
A FIB. AN UNTRUTH.

13:31.549 --> 13:32.637
I MADE IT UP.

13:32.681 --> 13:34.204
HAVE A SEAT.
I'LL EXPLAIN.

13:38.469 --> 13:40.254
DO EITHER OF YOU NOTICE
THE DIFFERENCE

13:40.297 --> 13:42.909
FROM THIS PHOTO
TO THIS PHOTO?

13:42.952 --> 13:44.649
WHERE'S WALDO?

13:44.693 --> 13:46.347
THERE'S A LIGHT BULB
ON THE SIGN

13:46.390 --> 13:48.523
THAT'S OFF IN ONE PHOTO
AND ON IN THE OTHER.

13:48.566 --> 13:50.264
SO THEY HAD
A BROKEN LIGHT BULB.

13:50.307 --> 13:53.267
BUT THEN
IT'S ON AGAIN HERE...

13:53.310 --> 13:54.834
AND OFF...

13:54.877 --> 13:57.793
AND ON.

13:57.837 --> 13:59.882
IT'S A SIGNAL.

13:59.926 --> 14:02.232
WHEN THE LIGHT IS ON,
THEY'RE SELLING DRUGS.

14:02.276 --> 14:03.799
WHEN IT'S OFF,
THEY'RE NOT.

14:03.843 --> 14:06.019
THIS PHOTO WAS TAKEN THE DAY
OF YOUR RAID.

14:06.062 --> 14:07.890
YOU NOTICE
HOW THE LIGHT IS OFF?

14:07.934 --> 14:10.066
AND THAT'S WHY YOU GUYS
DIDN'T FIND ANYTHING.

14:10.110 --> 14:11.111
THEY WEREN'T SELLING.

14:11.154 --> 14:13.461
BUT WHY THAT DAY, HUH?

14:13.504 --> 14:15.593
WAS IT JUST BAD LUCK?

14:15.637 --> 14:17.073
HERE WE ARE.

14:17.117 --> 14:20.120
12:00 ON THE DOT.

14:25.255 --> 14:28.519
THE GREEN LIGHT
IS ONTODAY.

14:28.563 --> 14:30.304
I TURNED IT ON.

14:30.347 --> 14:32.915
BUT WHAT DO YOU THINK
KORBELL IS GONNA DO

14:32.959 --> 14:35.483
WHEN HE THINKS
ANOTHER RAID IS COMING?

14:38.268 --> 14:40.227
ET VOILà.

14:40.270 --> 14:42.055
WAIT A MINUTE.

14:42.098 --> 14:44.622
HOW COULD KORBELL
KNOWTHAT?

14:44.666 --> 14:46.537
HE HAS AN INSIDE SOURCE.

14:46.581 --> 14:47.974
SOMEONE FROM D.E.A.

14:48.017 --> 14:51.064
AND IF I FIGURED IT OUT,
GONZALEZ DID.

14:51.107 --> 14:53.457
THAT'S WHAT
GOT HIM KILLED.

14:53.501 --> 14:56.504
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

14:56.547 --> 14:59.768
THAT SOMEONE ON YOUR TEAM
IS A KILLER.

15:08.124 --> 15:10.953
SO, WE'RE LOOKING FOR A COP
THAT KILLED A COP.

15:10.997 --> 15:12.781
GONZALEZ MUST HAVE FIGURED OUT
THERE WAS A MOLE.

15:12.824 --> 15:15.044
THE MOLE KILLED HIM
BEFORE HE COULD GO PUBLIC.

15:15.088 --> 15:16.828
WHOEVER IT IS,
HE'S BEEN AT IT A WHILE.

15:16.872 --> 15:18.439
THERE HAVE BEEN A HALF A DOZEN
BUSTED RAIDS

15:18.482 --> 15:19.701
IN THE PAST TWO YEARS.

15:19.744 --> 15:21.964
PETERSON'S EXPLAINED
THEM ALL AWAY --

15:22.008 --> 15:24.445
BAD INTEL, TACTICAL MISTAKES.

15:24.488 --> 15:27.100
IN HINDSIGHT, IT HAD TO HAVE
BEEN AN INSIDE MAN.

15:27.143 --> 15:28.797
SO FOR NOW
WE DON'T RULE OUT ANYONE.

15:28.840 --> 15:30.755
IT COULD BE ANY ONE
OF PETERSON'S AGENTS.

15:30.799 --> 15:31.756
THAT'S 30 SUSPECTS.

15:31.800 --> 15:34.281
31.
YOU FORGOT PETERSON.

15:34.324 --> 15:36.326
BILL PETERSON DOESN'T HAVE
MUCH OF A BEDSIDE MANNER,

15:36.370 --> 15:37.632
BUT HE'S NOT A TRAITOR.

15:37.675 --> 15:39.460
I THOUGHT WE COULDN'T
RULE ANYONE OUT.

15:39.503 --> 15:41.462
Patrick:
ABBOTT'S RIGHT.

15:41.505 --> 15:43.420
PETERSON'S NOT A SUSPECT.

15:43.464 --> 15:47.816
GOOD. SO, WE'LL, UH,
JUST DIG DOWN INTO HIS TEAM.

15:47.859 --> 15:50.079
PERSONAL REVIEWS,
BANK RECORDS.

15:50.123 --> 15:52.212
ANYTHING THAT POINTS
TO A MOTIVE.

15:52.255 --> 15:54.388
EGO, REVENGE.
WHAT? YOU DISAGREE?

15:54.431 --> 15:57.695
WELL, THEY'RE ALL POORLY PAID
GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES.

15:57.739 --> 16:01.047
YOU'RE NOT GONNA HAVE TO DIG
TOO DEEP TO FIND MOTIVE.

16:01.090 --> 16:02.962
YOU HAVE A BETTER IDEA?

16:03.005 --> 16:04.702
MAYBE.

16:04.746 --> 16:08.880
BUT FIRST, I NEED SOMEONE
TO RUN AN ERRAND FOR ME.

16:11.318 --> 16:12.667
BACK AT THE D.E.A.,

16:12.710 --> 16:14.538
WHAT WERE YOU AND OROSCO
SAYING TO EACH OTHER?

16:14.582 --> 16:17.672
OH, HE WAS APOLOGIZING
FOR HIS PARTNER BEING A JERK.

16:17.715 --> 16:18.934
I SAID IT WAS FINE.

16:18.978 --> 16:20.283
¿NO HABLAS ESPAÑOL?

16:20.327 --> 16:22.590
UH, ME HABLO
AT A NINTH-GRADE LEVEL.

16:22.633 --> 16:24.113
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:24.157 --> 16:25.941
I CAN SAY "GRANDMOTHER"
AND "HALL PASS."

16:25.985 --> 16:27.856
DO YOU SPEAK ANY
OTHER LANGUAGES?

16:27.899 --> 16:29.423
I'M FLUENT IN PIG LATIN.

16:29.466 --> 16:31.860
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M NOT REALLY SURE THAT COUNTS.

16:31.903 --> 16:33.296
LISTEN, I WANTED --

16:33.340 --> 16:34.515
VEGA, I NEED YOU
TO DO SOMETHING.

16:34.558 --> 16:35.864
BUT FIRST, A QUESTION.

16:35.907 --> 16:37.126
UH, WE SHOOT NEW PICTURES

16:37.170 --> 16:38.432
FOR THE I.D. BADGES
EVERY YEAR.

16:38.475 --> 16:40.086
DOES EVERY FEDERAL AGENCY
DO THAT?

16:40.129 --> 16:41.565
I THINK SO.
EXCELLENT.

16:41.609 --> 16:43.611
I NEED YOU TO GO BACK
TO SAN ANTONIO.

16:43.654 --> 16:47.006
I NEED YOU TO GET ALL PHOTO
I.D.s FOR PETERSON'S D.E.A. TEAM

16:47.049 --> 16:48.398
FOR THE PAST THREE YEARS.

16:48.442 --> 16:50.009
WE JUST GOT BACK
FROM SAN ANTONIO.

16:50.052 --> 16:52.185
I KNOW.

16:52.228 --> 16:54.361
NO REST FOR THE WEARY
CRIMEFIGHTER.

16:54.404 --> 16:56.537
SEE YOU WHEN I GET BACK.YEAH.

16:59.844 --> 17:02.586
[ PHONE RINGS ]

17:04.240 --> 17:05.459
ABBOTT.

17:05.502 --> 17:06.851
PETERSON: Dennis.

17:06.895 --> 17:07.983
I'M IN AUSTIN.

17:08.027 --> 17:09.854
LIKE TO TALK,
IF YOU GOT A MINUTE.

17:09.898 --> 17:11.987
SURE.
COME BY THE OFFICE.

17:12.031 --> 17:14.642
ACTUALLY, I'D PREFER TALKING
OUTSIDE YOUR OFFICE.

17:14.685 --> 17:17.079
Mind meeting me
at Graham Plaza?

17:19.125 --> 17:22.519
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

17:22.563 --> 17:23.999
EVENING, BILL.

17:24.043 --> 17:25.609
UH, YOU WANT A DRINK?

17:25.653 --> 17:28.134
CLUB SODA. THANKS.ANOTHER ONE.

17:30.179 --> 17:32.094
A HELL OF A THING TO KNOW

17:32.138 --> 17:35.097
THAT ONE OF YOUR PEOPLE
BETRAYED YOU.

17:35.141 --> 17:37.578
KILLED A COLLEAGUE.
A FRIEND.

17:37.621 --> 17:39.449
YEAH, IT'S HARD, I KNOW.

17:39.493 --> 17:41.669
YOU DIDN'T TELL
YOUR TEAM ANYTHING?

17:41.712 --> 17:43.236
NO.

17:43.279 --> 17:45.847
THEY THINK IT'S AN INVESTIGATION
OF A CARTEL MURDER.

17:45.890 --> 17:48.328
WELL, MY PEOPLE
ARE THE BEST, BILL.

17:48.371 --> 17:49.720
WE'LL GET THIS GUY.

17:49.764 --> 17:52.767
I'M SURE YOU WILL.

17:52.810 --> 17:55.987
WHEN YOU DO,
I NEED TO SHARE THE COLLAR.

17:56.031 --> 17:58.338
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

17:58.381 --> 18:00.253
I WANT CREDIT
FOR THE ARREST.

18:00.296 --> 18:02.559
WE'LL COME UP
WITH SOMETHING I DID --

18:02.603 --> 18:05.388
SOMETHING VITAL TO THE
INVESTIGATION, YOU KNOW.

18:05.432 --> 18:07.521
SO YOU WANT ME
TO LIE FOR YOU.

18:07.564 --> 18:09.131
I TOLD YOU, I HAVE ENEMIES.

18:09.175 --> 18:12.091
THEY FIND OUT ONE OF MY PEOPLE
WAS WORKING FOR THE CARTEL,

18:12.134 --> 18:14.615
THEY'LL TAKE ME TO TOWN
UNLESS I DO SOMETHING.

18:14.658 --> 18:16.573
I NEED TO BE PART
OF THE SOLUTION.

18:16.617 --> 18:18.575
YOU HAVE BEEN ASLEEP
AT THE WHEEL.

18:18.619 --> 18:20.621
ONE OF YOUR PEOPLE
HAS BEEN IN BED

18:20.664 --> 18:23.493
WITH THE SOSAS FOR TWO YEARS,
AND YOU DIDN'T SEE IT.

18:23.537 --> 18:25.495
NOW YOU WANT ME
TO COVER YOUR ASS?

18:25.539 --> 18:28.890
WE SHOULD BE HAVING A DISCUSSION
ABOUT YOUR RESIGNATION.

18:28.933 --> 18:33.547
WE'VE ALL DONE THINGS
WE'RE NOT PROUD OF, DENNIS --

18:33.590 --> 18:37.507
THINGS WE'D LIKE
KEPT QUIET.

18:41.468 --> 18:44.949
SO YOU'RE GONNA HANG RIO BRAVO
OVER MY HEAD

18:44.993 --> 18:46.603
UNLESS I PLAY ALONG.

18:46.647 --> 18:49.302
I WISH IT WAS JUST YOU.

18:49.345 --> 18:54.263
LENA'S CONFIRMATION IS COMING UP
IN A COUPLE OF WEEKS, RIGHT?

18:54.307 --> 19:00.356
RIO BRAVO COULD BE
A REAL PROBLEM THERE, TOO.

19:05.579 --> 19:08.538
I NEEDTHIS, DENNIS.

19:10.540 --> 19:12.020
KEEP ME POSTED.

19:29.080 --> 19:31.213
YOU READY
TO GET OUT OF HERE?

19:31.257 --> 19:33.520
UH, I THINK
I'M GONNA STICK AROUND.

19:33.563 --> 19:35.217
OKAY.

19:35.261 --> 19:37.132
ANY GUESSES ABOUT YOUR PRESENT?
OR HAVE YOU GIVEN UP?

19:37.176 --> 19:40.875
DOES IT WEIGH MORE OR LESS
THAN 3 1/2 POUNDS?

19:40.918 --> 19:42.268
WHY 3 1/2 POUNDS?

19:42.311 --> 19:44.008
BECAUSE.
LESS.

19:44.052 --> 19:45.880
IS IT MADE OF KRYPTONITE?
NO.

19:45.923 --> 19:49.100
IS IT SOMETHING THAT I WOULD
WEAR ON A COLD WINTER'S DAY?

19:49.144 --> 19:50.363
NO.

19:55.803 --> 19:59.241
THATIS MY GUESS.

19:59.285 --> 20:02.157
PROMISE ME YOU WILL NOT OPEN IT
TILL TOMORROW NIGHT.

20:02.201 --> 20:03.637
YOU ARE SO BLUFFING.
AREN'T YOU?

20:03.680 --> 20:05.291
SEE YOU LATER.

20:05.334 --> 20:06.466
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

20:18.173 --> 20:23.047
I'M GUESSING BY YOUR LOOK THAT
YOU JUST TALKED TO PETERSON.

20:24.353 --> 20:26.225
I'M LISTENING.

20:30.446 --> 20:32.970
I WORKED FOR HIM
ABOUT TEN YEARS AGO

20:33.014 --> 20:36.104
WHEN HE WAS RUNNING A TASK FORCE
ON THE BORDER.

20:36.147 --> 20:37.932
RIO BRAVO STATION.

20:40.369 --> 20:42.284
WE WERE WORKING
WITH THE MEXICAN POLICE,

20:42.328 --> 20:44.286
TRYING TO DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THE CARTELS.

20:44.330 --> 20:46.070
TOUGH WORK.

20:46.114 --> 20:47.289
IT WAS WAR.

20:49.857 --> 20:54.427
THE ZETA CARTEL WOULD SEND THEIR
MEN OUT DRESSED LIKE SOLDIERS.

20:54.470 --> 20:57.647
THEY WOULD WAIT FOR A BUS
TO COME THROUGH,

20:57.691 --> 21:02.043
STOP IT, FORCE ALL
THE PASSENGERS OFF,

21:02.086 --> 21:03.914
AND SHOOT THEM.

21:03.958 --> 21:05.612
ALL OF THEM.

21:05.655 --> 21:09.877
JUST SO THEY DIDN'T WORK
FOR ANOTHER CARTEL.

21:09.920 --> 21:12.923
THERE WERE
BODIES EVERYWHERE.

21:12.967 --> 21:16.927
MEN, WOMEN, CHILDREN...

21:16.971 --> 21:22.237
SCATTERED ALL OVER THE ROAD
LIKE TRASH.

21:22.281 --> 21:24.152
YEAH, IT'S --
IT'S NO PICTURE

21:24.195 --> 21:26.502
THAT ANYONE SHOULD HAVE
IN THEIR HEAD.

21:26.546 --> 21:32.203
ONE DAY I WAS SITTING
ON A ZETA SAFE HOUSE --

21:32.247 --> 21:36.904
JUST WATCHING
WHO CAME AND WENT.

21:36.947 --> 21:39.298
GATHERING INTEL.

21:41.212 --> 21:44.390
AND I SAW THIS...

21:44.433 --> 21:46.783
ZETA COMMANDER WALK OUT.

21:46.827 --> 21:48.829
DRESSED
IN A MILITARY UNIFORM.

21:48.872 --> 21:53.616
AND I KNEW
WHAT HE WAS GOING TO DO.

21:53.660 --> 21:55.879
I COULDN'T CALL
THE LOCAL POLICE

21:55.923 --> 21:58.621
BECAUSE THEY WERE TERRIFIED
OF THE ZETAS.

21:58.665 --> 22:00.144
I COULDN'T ARREST HIM.

22:00.188 --> 22:05.759
SO I SAT THERE, THINKING --
I DON'T KNOW --

22:05.802 --> 22:07.717
MAYBE THREE SECONDS.

22:09.980 --> 22:11.808
I GOT OUT OF MY CAR,

22:11.852 --> 22:15.812
I WALKED ACROSS THE STREET,
AND I SHOT HIM.

22:22.428 --> 22:24.908
YOU...

22:24.952 --> 22:27.911
YOU DID THE RIGHT THING.

22:30.479 --> 22:32.960
I DON'T KNOW.

22:33.003 --> 22:37.268
BUT NO BUSES WERE STOPPED
THAT NIGHT.

22:37.312 --> 22:41.098
AND THE NEXT DAY I QUIT
THE RIO BRAVO STATION.

22:41.142 --> 22:43.797
DID PETERSON KNOW
WHAT YOU HAD DONE?

22:43.840 --> 22:47.191
HE GUESSED.

22:47.235 --> 22:51.326
THE DEATH OF A COMMANDER
HIT THE NEWS.

22:51.370 --> 22:54.155
TONS OF SPECULATION
ON WHO KILLED HIM.

22:54.198 --> 22:57.332
AND...PETERSON KNEW WHERE I WAS
WHEN IT HAPPENED.

22:57.376 --> 23:00.422
MM. AND NOW HE'S THREATENING YOU
TO DO WHAT HE SAYS.

23:00.466 --> 23:02.076
PETERSON CAN END MY CAREER.

23:02.119 --> 23:04.513
I CAN GO TO PRISON.

23:04.557 --> 23:07.560
BUT IT'S NOT JUST ABOUT ME.

23:07.603 --> 23:09.562
ANY MENTION OF THIS

23:09.605 --> 23:13.479
COULD END THINGS FOR LENA
BEFORE IT EVEN STARTS.

23:13.522 --> 23:16.090
WELL,
YOU CAN'T LET HIM DO IT.

23:16.133 --> 23:18.962
I APPRECIATE THE THOUGHT.

23:20.921 --> 23:23.402
HOW DO WE STOP HIM?

23:24.794 --> 23:26.448
I'M NOT SURE.

23:28.232 --> 23:29.625
YET.

23:31.932 --> 23:34.630
BUT WHEN I KNOW,
I'LL TELL YOU THE ANSWER.

23:53.301 --> 23:55.477
HEY, CAN YOU HELP ME
WITH SOMETHING?

23:55.521 --> 23:57.479
SURE.

23:57.523 --> 23:59.481
ABBOTT ASKED ME TO LOOK
INTO KORBELL'S RECORDS,

23:59.525 --> 24:02.179
SEE HOW HE'S COMMUNICATING WITH
HIS CONTACT ON PETERSON'S TEAM.

24:02.223 --> 24:05.835
I'VE LOOKED AT KORBELL'S
PHONE, E-MAILS, TEXTS.

24:05.879 --> 24:07.446
NOTHING JUMPS OUT.

24:07.489 --> 24:09.448
THEY'RE TOO SMART TO USE
SOMETHING THAT EASY TO GET INTO.

24:09.491 --> 24:12.015
THEY MUST HAVE BEEN MAKING
CONTACT SOMEHOW.CHECK HIS DAY-TO-DAY.

24:12.059 --> 24:13.495
WHAT WAS KORBELL LOOKING AT
ON THE WEB?

24:13.539 --> 24:15.889
BASED ON THE SITES
HE VISITS,

24:15.932 --> 24:17.194
HE'S A HOUSTON FAN.

24:17.238 --> 24:19.806
HE BUYS A LOT
OF PROTEIN POWDER.

24:19.849 --> 24:21.416
HE'S INTO PERSIAN LONGHAIRS.

24:21.460 --> 24:24.550
THE CATS?

24:24.593 --> 24:25.899
YEAH.
NO WAY.

24:25.942 --> 24:27.596
WAY.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.468
HE SPENDS A LOT OF TIME
ON A PERSIAN LONGHAIR WEBSITE.

24:29.511 --> 24:30.730
I'VE READ HIS FILE.

24:30.773 --> 24:31.687
THERE IS NO WAY KORBELL
IS INTO CATS.

24:31.731 --> 24:33.428
HE'S TOO MACHO,

24:33.472 --> 24:34.908
TOO DESPERATE FOR APPROVAL.

24:34.951 --> 24:36.518
MUST HAVE BEEN GOING THERE
FOR SOMETHING.

24:36.562 --> 24:37.606
MAYBE THEY'RE COMMUNICATING
THROUGH THE MESSAGE BOARDS.

24:37.650 --> 24:39.173
NOBODY WOULD LOOK
THERE FIRST.

24:39.216 --> 24:41.697
I'LL CHECK IT OUT.

24:43.438 --> 24:45.179
I GOT THE I.D. PICTURES.THANK YOU.

24:45.222 --> 24:48.138
THE PAST THREE YEARS FOR EACH
PERSON ON PETERSON'S TEAM.

24:48.182 --> 24:50.401
30 IN TOTAL.
MOST RECENT PICTURES ON TOP.

24:50.445 --> 24:52.403
YOU'RE A MARVEL, VEGA.
WELL DONE.

25:08.158 --> 25:09.812
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

25:09.856 --> 25:12.946
THEIR EYES.

25:12.989 --> 25:14.034
WINDOWS TO THE SOUL.

25:14.077 --> 25:15.165
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

25:15.209 --> 25:16.732
GOOD CALL, VEGA.

25:16.776 --> 25:18.386
REALLY,
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

25:18.429 --> 25:20.301
WELL, I DON'T WANT TO RUIN
THE SURPRISE,

25:20.344 --> 25:21.781
BUT SINCE
YOU'RE INTERESTED,

25:21.824 --> 25:23.652
THERE MAY BE SOMETHING
YOU CAN HELP ME WITH.

25:23.696 --> 25:24.914
REQUIRES SOME BRAVADO,

25:24.958 --> 25:26.699
WHICH SHOULD BE
RIGHT UP YOUR ALLEY.

25:26.742 --> 25:28.483
HELP YOU WITH WHAT?

25:28.527 --> 25:30.267
A LITTLE SOMETHING
TO CATCH A KILLER.

25:30.311 --> 25:33.923
YOU WANT ME TO HELP YOU
WITH A TRICK.

25:33.967 --> 25:35.838
WELL, IF THAT'S WHAT
YOU WANT TO CALL IT.

25:35.882 --> 25:37.144
PROBLEM?

25:38.885 --> 25:40.669
SPEAK YOUR MIND, SOLDIER.

25:42.932 --> 25:44.804
IT'S JUST --

25:44.847 --> 25:48.677
I VERY MUCH APPRECIATE BEING
A PART OF THIS TEAM, SIR.

25:48.721 --> 25:50.549
YOU GET RESULTS.

25:50.592 --> 25:52.942
I RESPECT THAT.THANK YOU. BUT?

25:52.986 --> 25:56.206
THE THINGS YOU ASK PEOPLE
TO DO --

25:56.250 --> 25:59.209
IT'S...
[ SIGHS ]

25:59.253 --> 26:02.691
IT'S NOT WHAT I THOUGHT WORKING
FOR THE FBI WOULD BE LIKE.

26:02.735 --> 26:03.866
AT ALL.

26:03.910 --> 26:05.476
NO.

26:05.520 --> 26:07.217
AND, UH, MORE IMPORTANTLY,

26:07.261 --> 26:10.090
YOU WONDER IF YOUR FATHER
WOULD APPROVE.

26:11.961 --> 26:13.572
SOMETIMES.

26:15.095 --> 26:16.662
HE WAS STRICT.

26:16.705 --> 26:18.838
37 YEARS IN THE MILITARY

26:18.881 --> 26:20.448
MAKES YOU A STICKLER
FOR THE RULES.

26:20.491 --> 26:22.189
I'M SURE HE WAS.

26:22.232 --> 26:24.147
AND A GOOD FATHER.

26:24.191 --> 26:26.628
AND YOU'RE PROOF OF THAT.

26:26.672 --> 26:29.022
BUT I CAN'T TELL YOU WHAT
YOUR FATHER WOULD APPROVE OF.

26:30.806 --> 26:34.505
THAT'S FOR YOU TO DECIDE.

26:39.032 --> 26:40.163
SIR?

26:40.207 --> 26:42.339
YES, VEGA?

26:42.383 --> 26:45.560
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

26:45.604 --> 26:49.303
WELL, WHEN I'M FINISHED HERE,
I'LL TELL YOU.

26:49.346 --> 26:52.436
SURE.

26:52.480 --> 26:53.916
[ DOOR OPENS ]

26:53.960 --> 26:56.179
THANK YOU.

26:56.223 --> 26:57.964
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

26:59.487 --> 27:03.709
[ PHONE RINGS ]

27:03.752 --> 27:05.319
ABBOTT.

27:05.362 --> 27:07.582
DENNIS, ANY PROGRESS?

27:07.626 --> 27:09.584
SOME.

27:09.628 --> 27:12.674
DON'T MAKE ME CHASE YOU DOWN.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

27:12.718 --> 27:14.807
WE'RE GATHERING
INFORMATION.

27:14.850 --> 27:17.679
Let me know as soon
as you got something.

27:17.723 --> 27:19.159
Don't hold out on me.

27:19.202 --> 27:21.422
THAT WILL NOTGO WELL.

27:31.693 --> 27:33.042
MAKING PROGRESS?

27:33.086 --> 27:34.348
YES, ACTUALLY.

27:34.391 --> 27:36.045
Wylie: GOT SOMETHING.

27:36.089 --> 27:38.395
KORBELL WAS TRADING MESSAGES
WITH HIS CONTACT

27:38.439 --> 27:40.397
ON PETERSON'S TEAM
THROUGH A CAT BLOG.

27:40.441 --> 27:41.790
WHAT WAS IN THE MESSAGES?

27:41.834 --> 27:44.184
CODED LANGUAGE
ABOUT D.E.A. INVESTIGATIONS.

27:44.227 --> 27:46.839
THE FIRST LETTER OF EACH WORD
SPELLS THE MESSAGE.

27:46.882 --> 27:48.231
SO, FOR INSTANCE...

27:48.275 --> 27:50.277
"REACTIVE ALLERGIES
IN DE-CLAWED ANIMALS?

27:50.320 --> 27:52.018
TRY 4
PREVENTATIVE MEASURES."

27:52.061 --> 27:54.803
THAT SPELLS "RAID AT 4PM."

27:54.847 --> 27:56.892
IT'S ACTUALLY PRETTY COOL.[ CHUCKLES ]

27:56.936 --> 27:58.502
DO WE KNOW WHO KORBELL
WAS DEALING WITH?
NO.

27:58.546 --> 27:59.939
WHOEVER IT IS
HAS COVERED HIS TRACKS

27:59.982 --> 28:01.027
WITH PROXY SERVERS AND VPNs.

28:01.070 --> 28:02.115
WHATEVER THEYARE.

28:02.158 --> 28:03.856
BUT HERE'S SOMETHING
INTERESTING.

28:03.899 --> 28:06.206
AS OF YESTERDAY,
HE SUDDENLY STOPPED POSTING.

28:06.249 --> 28:08.295
THERE ARE NO NEW MESSAGES.

28:08.338 --> 28:10.384
HE'S GETTING READY TO RUN.

28:10.427 --> 28:11.777
MAYBE HE'S JUST LAYING LOW.

28:11.820 --> 28:13.126
WELL, A POKER PLAYER
THAT STOPS BETTING

28:13.169 --> 28:14.605
ISN'T LAYING LOW.

28:14.649 --> 28:16.564
HE'S CASHING IN.

28:16.607 --> 28:17.913
WELL, IF HE'S ABOUT TO RABBIT,
THEN WE BETTER MOVE QUICKLY.

28:17.957 --> 28:19.567
IT'S PERFECT.
CALL SAN ANTONIO.

28:19.610 --> 28:21.743
TELL THEM THERE'S BEEN
A BREAKTHROUGH IN THE CASE.

28:21.787 --> 28:23.832
HAVE THEM GATHER UP
THESE TEN AGENTS,

28:23.876 --> 28:26.095
AND I'LL GO TALK TO THEM
IN TWO HOURS.

28:31.840 --> 28:36.540
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

28:38.020 --> 28:40.457
Cho:
EVERYBODY'S HERE.

28:40.501 --> 28:42.068
YOU NEEDN'T WORRY.

28:42.111 --> 28:43.939
I-I'M NOT WORRIED.

28:43.983 --> 28:46.942
GOOD.

28:46.986 --> 28:48.901
VEGA, YOU'RE ON.

28:48.944 --> 28:51.860
Just stay relaxed.
You'll be just fine.

28:51.904 --> 28:53.383
THANK YOU, SIR.

28:56.212 --> 28:57.431
[ SIGHS ]

28:57.474 --> 28:59.128
LET'S GO.

29:05.047 --> 29:07.615
AGENT PETERSON.

29:07.658 --> 29:10.096
YOU'RE ONE OF ABBOTT'S PEOPLE,
RIGHT?

29:11.575 --> 29:14.274
I'LL BE DOWN TO WHATEVER
HE'S DOING IN A MINUTE.

29:14.317 --> 29:17.407
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
ACTUALLY, SIR...

29:17.451 --> 29:19.670
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

29:22.456 --> 29:24.632
I'M WHAT?

29:24.675 --> 29:26.025
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

29:26.068 --> 29:27.156
COULD YOU ALL TAKE A SEAT

29:27.200 --> 29:28.244
UP FRONT HERE, PLEASE?

29:28.288 --> 29:29.550
THANK YOU.

29:33.206 --> 29:35.904
I KNOW YOU'RE WONDERING
WHY YOU'RE HERE.

29:35.948 --> 29:37.819
THE ANSWER TO THAT IS SIMPLE --

29:37.863 --> 29:40.343
ONE OF YOU KILLED
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

29:40.387 --> 29:42.781
[ AGENTS MURMUR ]

29:42.824 --> 29:45.348
AND I'M GONNA TELL YOU WHO
IN ABOUT FIVE MINUTES.

29:45.392 --> 29:47.524
AGENTS CHO AND LISBON WILL COME
THROUGH THE AISLES.

29:47.568 --> 29:49.526
WE'RE ASKING YOU
TO GIVE UP YOUR GUNS.

29:49.570 --> 29:51.311
YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

29:51.354 --> 29:53.487
WE'LL RETURN THE WEAPONS
WHEN THIS IS OVER.

29:53.530 --> 29:54.836
IF YOU'RE INNOCENT,
THERE'S NO PROBLEM.

29:54.880 --> 29:56.142
IF THERE'S A KILLER
IN THE ROOM,

29:56.185 --> 29:58.013
WE DON'T WANT TO RISK
A GUN FIGHT.

29:58.057 --> 29:59.841
WE DON'T WANT ANYONE
TO GET HURT.

29:59.885 --> 30:01.364
I'M AFRAID I HAVE TO INSIST.

30:01.408 --> 30:03.671
ONE OF YOU IS WORKING
WITH THE SOSA CARTEL

30:03.714 --> 30:05.542
AND BETRAYED YOUR TEAM.

30:05.586 --> 30:08.023
IF YOU'RE NOT INTERESTED
IN KNOWING WHO THAT PERSON IS,

30:08.067 --> 30:09.808
BY ALL MEANS, KEEP YOUR GUNS.

30:14.290 --> 30:17.511
[ GUNS THUDDING LIGHTLY ]

30:24.213 --> 30:25.824
THANK YOU.

30:42.275 --> 30:44.146
QUESTION --

30:44.190 --> 30:46.192
HAVE ANY OF YOU
RECENTLY INHERITED

30:46.235 --> 30:48.934
SOME MONEY FROM A DECEASED
PARENT OR GRANDPARENT?

30:48.977 --> 30:51.023
I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT A LITTLE BIT.

30:51.066 --> 30:53.155
A PILE,
ENOUGH TO MAKE A DIFFERENCE.

30:53.199 --> 30:54.461
RAISE YOUR HANDS, PLEASE.

30:54.504 --> 30:56.245
DON'T BE SHY.

30:56.289 --> 31:00.597
I'M VERY SORRY FOR YOUR LOSSES.

31:00.641 --> 31:02.643
UH, NONE OF YOU KILLED
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

31:02.686 --> 31:04.471
YOU CAN MOVE TO THE BACK
OF THE ROOM, PLEASE.

31:04.514 --> 31:06.342
THANK YOU.

31:06.386 --> 31:09.868
WHAT DOES AN INHERITANCE HAVE
TO DO WITH WHO KILLED GONZALEZ?

31:09.911 --> 31:11.217
THAT IS A GOOD QUESTION.

31:11.260 --> 31:13.567
BUT I AM THE ONE
ASKING THOSE RIGHT NOW.

31:13.610 --> 31:16.309
NOW, IS THERE ANYONE HERE
IN A RELATIONSHIP

31:16.352 --> 31:18.615
WITH SOMEONE
FROM THE BEAUTY FIELD?

31:18.659 --> 31:20.922
Man: YEAH.

31:20.966 --> 31:23.751
MY HUSBAND RUNS A COUPLE
OF STYLING SALONS.

31:23.794 --> 31:25.144
HOW LONG HAVE YOU
BEEN TOGETHER?

31:25.187 --> 31:26.885
A YEAR.

31:26.928 --> 31:28.887
CONGRATULATIONS.
I'M VERY HAPPY FOR YOU.

31:28.930 --> 31:30.801
UM, YOU DIDN'T KILL
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

31:30.845 --> 31:33.152
WOULD YOU MOVE TO THE BACK
OF THE ROOM, PLEASE?

31:34.893 --> 31:39.027
ANYONE HERE GET DIVORCED
IN THE PAST THREE YEARS?

31:40.550 --> 31:42.639
YES, LAW ENFORCEMENT --
TOUGH ON THE HOME LIFE.

31:42.683 --> 31:44.903
ON THE PLUS SIDE,
YOU DIDN'T KILL GONZALEZ.

31:44.946 --> 31:47.035
BACK YOU GO, PLEASE.[ Sighing ] OH. WOW.

31:47.079 --> 31:49.211
YOU THINK ONE OF USARE IN BED
WITH THE SOSAS?

31:49.255 --> 31:50.996
THAT'S CRAZY.

31:51.039 --> 31:52.171
REALLY.
WHY WOULD WE DO THAT?

31:52.214 --> 31:53.563
MONEY, I ASSUME.

31:53.607 --> 31:54.738
BUT I-I DON'T CARE
ABOUT THE MOTIVE.

31:54.782 --> 31:57.654
I'M INTERESTED
IN WHAT HAPPENED

31:57.698 --> 31:59.613
AFTER ONE OF YOU
BECAME A TRAITOR.

31:59.656 --> 32:02.529
I LOOKED AT YOUR I.D. PICTURES
FOR THE LAST FEW YEARS.

32:02.572 --> 32:05.010
ALL TEN OF YOU HAVE IMPROVED
YOUR APPEARANCE,

32:05.053 --> 32:07.969
MOST NOTICEABLY BY SPRUCING UP
YOUR HAIR.

32:08.013 --> 32:10.102
SOME OF YOU BECAUSE
YOU INHERITED MONEY,

32:10.145 --> 32:12.539
OTHERS BECAUSE YOU'RE BACK
IN THE DATING SCENE.

32:12.582 --> 32:15.237
ARE YOU SERIOUSLY SAYING
THAT ONE OF US IS THE KILLER

32:15.281 --> 32:17.022
BECAUSE WE GOT
A BETTER HAIRCUT?

32:17.065 --> 32:20.677
A KILLER, NO.
A TRAITOR, YES.

32:20.721 --> 32:24.420
WHOEVER SOLD OUT TO THE SOSAS
MADE BANK

32:24.464 --> 32:27.162
AND GOT A BIG EGO BOOST.

32:27.206 --> 32:30.122
WHEN YOU HAVE A GOOD SECRET,
IT MAKES YOU FEEL IMPORTANT.

32:30.165 --> 32:32.428
IF YOU'RE SO SURE,
WHICH ONE OF US IS IT?

32:32.472 --> 32:35.866
WELL, THAT'S THE QUESTION,
ISN'T IT?

32:35.910 --> 32:37.651
JANE.

32:37.694 --> 32:38.608
JUST A MINUTE, VEGA.

32:38.652 --> 32:39.870
I FOUND THE KILLER.

32:42.569 --> 32:43.962
IT'S BILL PETERSON.

32:44.005 --> 32:45.964
[ GRUNTS ]

32:54.581 --> 32:57.105
YOU'RE SERIOUSLY DOING THIS.

32:57.149 --> 32:59.803
I WAS CERTAIN IT WAS GONNA BE
ONE OF THE OTHER THREE AGENTS.

32:59.847 --> 33:00.891
ARE WE SURE ABOUT THIS?

33:00.935 --> 33:02.415
WYLIE FOUND A LINK

33:02.458 --> 33:04.025
THROUGH THE CAT BLOG TO AN
OFFSHORE ACCOUNT IN BELIZE.

33:04.069 --> 33:06.245
IT WAS HIDDEN UNDER ALIASES
AND SHELLS,

33:06.288 --> 33:08.029
BUT HE TRACED IT BACK
TO PETERSON.

33:08.073 --> 33:10.031
3.2 MILLION BUCKS.

33:10.075 --> 33:14.209
YOU'RE ACCUSING ME --
GET YOUR PEOPLE IN LINE!

33:14.253 --> 33:15.689
TAKE HIM OUT OF HERE.

33:15.732 --> 33:17.038
ABBOTT...

33:17.082 --> 33:19.693
YOU THINK I'M GONNA FORGET
ABOUT THIS, HUH?

33:19.736 --> 33:21.129
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?!

33:21.173 --> 33:22.826
YOU HAVE EVIDENCE
AGAINST AGENT PETERSON?

33:22.870 --> 33:24.828
YOU CAN PICK UP YOUR FIREARMS
ON THE WAY OUT.

33:24.872 --> 33:26.004
WE'RE DONE HERE.

33:32.836 --> 33:34.534
BORDICK.

33:34.577 --> 33:36.536
YEAH?

33:36.579 --> 33:38.016
YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU'RE IN A HURRY.

33:38.059 --> 33:39.800
WHAT'S THE RUSH?

33:39.843 --> 33:43.064
NOTHING.
I MEAN [Chuckling] NONE.

33:43.108 --> 33:44.805
YOU GOT A GO-BAG IN YOUR TRUNK,
DON'T YOU?

33:44.848 --> 33:46.807
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

33:46.850 --> 33:50.071
YOU KILLED
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

33:50.115 --> 33:52.030
WHERE ARE YOU HEADED?

33:52.073 --> 33:54.554
THE GULF?

33:54.597 --> 33:56.077
AIRPORT?

33:56.121 --> 33:58.166
WHY WOULD I BE GOING
TO THE GULF?

33:58.210 --> 34:00.081
YOU KILLED
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

34:02.736 --> 34:06.174
SO YOU THOUGHT YOU WERE
GONNA GET AWAY?

34:06.218 --> 34:08.437
EXCUSE ME?

34:08.481 --> 34:10.222
WHEN WE ARRESTED PETERSON,

34:10.265 --> 34:12.050
YOU THOUGHT YOU HAD TIME
TO ESCAPE.

34:12.093 --> 34:13.573
BUT I KNOW WHAT YOU DID.

34:13.616 --> 34:15.314
WHAT?

34:15.357 --> 34:18.099
YOU KILLED
DARRELL GONZALEZ.

34:18.143 --> 34:19.448
NO. PETERSON DID.

34:19.492 --> 34:21.885
YOU GUYS SAID SO.
YOU ARRESTED HIM.

34:21.929 --> 34:23.626
IT WAS YOU.

34:23.670 --> 34:25.106
I'M NOT LETTING YOU ALONE
UNTIL I PROVE IT.

34:25.150 --> 34:27.065
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

34:27.108 --> 34:31.417
I AM GOING TO TAIL YOU EVERY DAY
UNTIL YOU'RE IN CUFFS.

34:31.460 --> 34:33.375
I DON'T CARE
HOW LONG IT TAKES.

34:33.419 --> 34:35.290
I AM GONNA PUT YOU
BEHIND BARS.

34:35.334 --> 34:36.987
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

34:39.773 --> 34:41.644
LISBON.

34:41.688 --> 34:45.648
[ Man speaking indistinctly ]

34:45.692 --> 34:49.130
[ CELLPHONE BUZZES ]

34:49.174 --> 34:52.220
THIS IS ABBOTT.

34:52.264 --> 34:53.526
[ Man speaking indistinctly ]

34:53.569 --> 34:55.049
CHO.

34:55.093 --> 34:56.442
[ Man speaking indistinctly ]

34:56.485 --> 34:59.836
[ CLICK, GUNSHOT ]

35:02.665 --> 35:03.840
BLANKS.

35:07.322 --> 35:09.629
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

35:25.558 --> 35:26.950
WE FOUND YOUR GO-BAG.

35:26.994 --> 35:29.518
YEAH, QUITE THE TRIP
YOU WERE PLANNING.

35:29.562 --> 35:32.391
FAKE PASSPORT,
CROATIAN KUNAS.

35:32.434 --> 35:33.914
HEY, LISBON, DOES CROATIA

35:33.957 --> 35:35.785
HAVE AN EXTRADITION TREATY
WITH THE U.S.?

35:35.829 --> 35:37.787
I DON'T BELIEVE THEY DO.

35:37.831 --> 35:40.181
WE ALSO FOUND
THE TRACKING PROGRAM

35:40.225 --> 35:42.705
YOU INSTALLED
ON GONZALEZ'S COMPUTER.

35:42.749 --> 35:44.272
HE'D SUSPECTED A MOLE.

35:44.316 --> 35:47.493
IT WAS ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE HE LATCHED ON TO YOU.

35:47.536 --> 35:50.017
SO, WHY DID YOU START WORKING
FOR THE SOSAS?

35:50.060 --> 35:52.019
WHY BETRAY YOUR TEAM?

35:52.062 --> 35:53.760
MY TEAM?

35:53.803 --> 35:55.936
I'VE BEEN AT D.E.A.
FOR SIX YEARS.

35:55.979 --> 35:58.025
YOU KNOW HOW MANY TIMES
MY "TEAM"

35:58.068 --> 36:00.201
HAS PASSED ME OVER
FOR PROMOTIONS?

36:00.245 --> 36:02.421
SO YOU WANTED TO SHOW THEM
HOW SMART YOU ARE?

36:02.464 --> 36:04.423
NO, WAIT A MINUTE.
HE COULDN'T BE THAT SMART.

36:04.466 --> 36:06.468
I MEAN, WE CAUGHT YOU.

36:06.512 --> 36:08.122
TOOK YOU YEARS.

36:08.166 --> 36:11.821
THAT WHOLE TIME,
I WAS TIPPING OFF DEALERS,

36:11.865 --> 36:15.129
RUINING BUSTS,
STASHING PAYOFFS.

36:15.173 --> 36:17.697
I WAS THE MOST POWERFUL GUY
IN THAT BUILDING.

36:17.740 --> 36:20.526
NOBODY KNEW.

36:20.569 --> 36:23.093
SO WHO'S THE SMART ONE?

36:23.137 --> 36:26.445
LET'S GET THIS SMART MAN
A NICE JAIL CELL.

36:30.971 --> 36:33.408
[ DOOR OPENS ]

36:33.452 --> 36:37.499
Dennis: WE FOUND ENOUGH EVIDENCE
IN OROSCO'S APARTMENT

36:37.543 --> 36:41.199
TO ARREST KORBELL AND SEVERAL
OF HIS EMPLOYEES.

36:41.242 --> 36:44.985
KORBELL'S GOING TO FLIP
AGAINST THE SOSA CARTEL.

36:45.028 --> 36:47.422
FEELS LIKE A WIN,
ALL IN ALL.

36:47.466 --> 36:49.468
YOU HUMILIATED ME
IN FRONT OF MY PEOPLE!

36:49.511 --> 36:52.079
YOU PERP-WALKED ME
THROUGH MY OWN OFFICE!

36:52.122 --> 36:54.560
WE HAD TO MAKE OROSCO FEEL LIKE
HE HAD A CHANCE TO GET AWAY.

36:54.603 --> 36:56.257
YOU WERE THE MISDIRECTION.

36:56.301 --> 36:58.259
IT'S NOT THE BEST PART,
BUT YOU PLAYED IT ADEQUATELY.

36:58.303 --> 37:00.218
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO TELL ME
WHAT YOU WERE DOING.

37:00.261 --> 37:01.828
WE COULDN'T DO THAT.
YOU WOULD HAVE BLOWN THE SHOT.

37:01.871 --> 37:03.003
I MEAN, OBVIOUSLY.

37:03.046 --> 37:05.571
LOOK, I'M SORRY, BILL.
REALLY, I AM.

37:05.614 --> 37:07.486
I WAS SUPPOSED
TO GET THE CREDIT!

37:07.529 --> 37:08.356
WE HAD A DEAL!

37:08.400 --> 37:09.705
THERE WAS NO DEAL, BILL.

37:09.749 --> 37:11.881
JUST A CRAZY IDEA YOU HAD
IN YOUR HEAD.

37:11.925 --> 37:13.405
YOU'RE DONE,ABBOTT.

37:13.448 --> 37:15.537
IT'S OVER FOR YOU
ANDYOUR WIFE.

37:15.581 --> 37:17.235
I'M GONNA SEE TO THAT.

37:17.278 --> 37:19.541
OKAY. I'VE BEEN PATIENT.
I'VE BEEN POLITE.

37:19.585 --> 37:21.891
NOT ANYMORE.
TAKE IT BACK.

37:23.066 --> 37:24.764
WHAT?!

37:24.807 --> 37:28.202
TAKE BACK YOUR LITTLE THREAT
AND APOLOGIZE TO MY FRIEND HERE.

37:28.246 --> 37:29.290
WHY?

37:29.334 --> 37:32.380
THIS DISPLAY, THIS TANTRUM --

37:32.424 --> 37:35.122
IT ISN'T ABOUT ANGER, IS IT?
IT'S ABOUT FEAR.

37:35.165 --> 37:37.516
FEAR? OF WHAT?

37:37.559 --> 37:39.082
THAT WE WEREN'T TOO FAR OFF

37:39.126 --> 37:41.520
ABOUT YOU KEEPING A STASH
OF DIRTY MONEY,

37:41.563 --> 37:44.087
AND THAT WITH ENOUGH TIME,
WE WILL FIND IT.

37:44.131 --> 37:45.611
[ SIGHS ]

37:46.829 --> 37:50.529
GIVE MY BEST TO LENA.

37:52.966 --> 37:54.924
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

37:54.968 --> 37:56.883
ABSOLUTELY.

37:56.926 --> 37:59.799
WE HAVE HIM
RIGHT WHERE WE WANT HIM.

37:59.842 --> 38:01.888
NO, I HEARD YOU WERE AWESOME
DOWN THERE.

38:01.931 --> 38:03.237
REALLY?

38:03.281 --> 38:04.630
OH, BECAUSE I FELT LIKE

38:04.673 --> 38:06.501
I WAS GOING TO THROW UP
THE WHOLE TIME.

38:06.545 --> 38:08.242
LISBON SAID YOU NAILED
ARRESTING PETERSON.

38:08.286 --> 38:09.765
LIKE A PRO.

38:09.809 --> 38:11.332
WELL, IT WAS ACTUALLY FUN.

38:11.376 --> 38:14.553
I DIDN'T THINK IT WOULD BE,
BUT, UH, IT WAS.

38:14.596 --> 38:16.729
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

38:18.731 --> 38:20.559
OH, GOD.

38:20.602 --> 38:22.343
WHAT?

38:22.387 --> 38:24.476
UM...

38:24.519 --> 38:27.609
IT'S BORDICK,
FROM SAN ANTONIO D.E.A.

38:27.653 --> 38:30.482
HE'S...ASKING ME OUT.

38:30.525 --> 38:33.615
OH.

38:33.659 --> 38:36.052
FORTUNATELY, I CAN HONESTLY
TELL HIM I HAVE NO INTEREST.

38:38.141 --> 38:39.708
I AM SO NOT INTO THAT
RIGHT NOW.

38:39.752 --> 38:41.231
I JUST WANT
TO FOCUS ON WORK.

38:41.275 --> 38:43.277
SURE.

38:43.321 --> 38:44.974
KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

38:45.018 --> 38:47.325
YEAH. TOTALLY.

38:47.368 --> 38:48.848
ME TOO.

38:48.891 --> 38:52.373
UM, I AM TAKING THESE FILES
DOWN TO ADMIN.

38:52.417 --> 38:54.767
BUT WILL YOU BE HERE LATER?

38:54.810 --> 38:56.203
ALMOST CERTAINLY.

38:56.246 --> 38:58.379
SEE YOU.

39:01.513 --> 39:03.428
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

39:05.734 --> 39:07.519
THE LIGHTS
ARE A NICE TOUCH.

39:07.562 --> 39:09.869
MM.

39:09.912 --> 39:11.740
HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

39:11.784 --> 39:14.395
THANK YOU.

39:14.439 --> 39:17.398
MAKE A WISH.

39:21.794 --> 39:26.233
AND HEREIS YOUR GIFT.

39:29.584 --> 39:32.065
[ LAUGHS ] OPEN IT.

39:38.550 --> 39:40.334
[ SIGHS ]

39:46.775 --> 39:49.212
LISBON.

39:49.256 --> 39:52.912
THE ONE AND ONLY.
FROM THE CBI.

39:52.955 --> 39:55.218
YOU KEPT THE PIECES.

39:55.262 --> 39:56.524
YEAH.

39:56.568 --> 39:58.352
LOOKS PRETTY NICE,
DOESN'T IT?

39:58.396 --> 40:00.180
IT'S PERFECT.

40:00.223 --> 40:02.661
I'M SPEECHLESS.

40:02.704 --> 40:04.402
IT'S [SIGHS]

40:04.445 --> 40:07.883
YOU REALLY DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT IT WAS?

40:07.927 --> 40:10.973
YEAH,
YOU CAN SEE FOR YOURSELF.

40:16.892 --> 40:18.459
YOU REALLY DIDN'T KNOW?

40:18.503 --> 40:21.375
I'M GENUINELY SURPRISED.
THIS IS...

40:21.419 --> 40:24.465
[ SIGHS ]

40:24.509 --> 40:27.207
THIS IS SUCH
A BEAUTIFUL GIFT.

40:27.250 --> 40:29.035
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

40:29.078 --> 40:30.950
I'M AMAZED.

40:30.993 --> 40:33.735
BRAVO.

40:33.779 --> 40:35.345
ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE
NOT JUST PRETENDING

40:35.389 --> 40:36.956
YOU DIDN'T KNOW WHAT IT WAS
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER?

40:36.999 --> 40:38.479
BECAUSE YOU DON'T HAVE TO MAKE
ME FEEL BETTER.

40:38.523 --> 40:39.785
NO, COME ON, PLEASE.

40:39.828 --> 40:42.004
LISBON, JUST TAKE
THE COMPLIMENT.

40:42.048 --> 40:44.920
FINE.

40:44.964 --> 40:47.662
CHEERS.

40:47.706 --> 40:48.620
CHEERS.

40:48.663 --> 40:50.491
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

41:00.632 --> 41:02.155
[ SMOOCHES ]
